Lameɛna ma yella tneṭṭfem-ik iwumi qqaṛen Akniw, yețțunefk i wiyaḍ ad xedmen am nețța. Ɣef wayagi, ilaq a d-yas ad meqṛen di teṛwiḥt-nni isem-is, ad yili am tissas n tnezduɣt-nni.
Llant gar-asent tijmaɛin n wuzzal, ɣeṛqen meṛṛa ɣer tegmatin ; di tigzirt n jidayen n imawlan-nsen akk-d warraw n Sidna Ibṛahim di leɛmeṛ, iwumi d-yekker Yeɛqub akk-d wat Isṛail.
Ma d kečč yesɣaṛayen ul-ik tugiḍ aț-țbeddleḍ tikli, tețheggiḍ i yiman-ik lɛiqab ameqqran i wass n westeɛfu, daymi ur tețțut ara yid-es iwakken a d-yawi ɣer webrid n wass n westeɛfu.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Luri, feccal, ɣef ddemma n limin i s-d-izzin i ukersi n lḥekma di tmurt-nni, i genneɛtaben iman-nsen ɣef tbuciḍant-is.
Imdanen-agi am tliwa iqquṛen, am usigna y
Mkul Tafaska n izimer n leslak Bilaṭus yețserriḥ-ed i yiwen umeḥbus.
Aṭas n wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Baba Ṛebbi ț-țzemmar n igenwan. Ger wid ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi, i gzedɣen di tmurt n ddunit ; wid ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad uɣalen d iɛdawen n Lmasiḥ akk-d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ.
Di tudert-agi tajdiṭ ulac win ara d-yesfehmen ; am akken tewjed leḥjab-nni urrif n Lmasiḥ, ɣeṛqenbeɣ a d-iban tafat seg wefṛaḥ n tafat.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : imasiḥiyen n Lmasiḥ ițwasemmṛen ɣef wumidag, eɛni ur nelli ara d win n wat Isṛail seg wasmi i d-ffɣen seg wesfel ;
Lmasiḥ, țextiṛin imukan imezwura di lebḥeṛ, di tmeɣṛiwin, n tejmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, nnejmaɛen-d iwakken a d-ḥeṛṛek m'ara d-yaweḍ lɛid n Tfaska.
Taɣuṛfeț anda i nennejmaɛ, ceɛlent deg-s kra n teftilin, ɣeṛqent amek ara yilin fell-aɣ.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d mmi-s, imeḥbas meṛṛa n lewqat i d-iteffɣen seg wezṛu alamma yekka-d sennig n temḍelt.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i lebḥeṛ n Jlili, yiwen wemkan-nni anda ara sseṛɣ imdanen aman amzun d ifṛax, leɛcuc-nsen s mkul ṣṣenf.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di leɛli, neɣ m'ulac a d-naɣ gar-awen m'ara tteḥyu a d-teḥyu si ddunit.
Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, yeɣli-d ṭṭlam ɣef wallen-is yiwen uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes, m'ara bɣun-ik, yewweḍ-ed lweqt aț-țemfaṛaqem ɣer igenni iwakken aț-țemfaṛaqem, aț-țemfaṛaqem ɣer mkul tama.
Deg ifragen-agi aṭas n imuḍan i gḍelqen, iderɣalen, iɛibanen d wukrifen țṛaǧun akk ad ḥerrken waman. ?čuṛen akk ɣer yiɣil n igenwan aț-țeččem.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, llan kra n yemdanen seg wid yeznuzun itbiren.
Aɛsekṛi i gebɣan ad yeɛǧeb i lqebṭan-nsen, ur ilaq ara ad ixemmem ɣef lecɣal n ddunit ; ad ɛawnen, ad setɛeṛfen s tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi ɣef wumidag, ad feṛqen llebsa-ines.
Sidi Ṛebbi yețțili lxilaf ger yemdanen, tețṛuḥun ɣer wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ iwakken ad frun tilufa-nwen !
Lmuqedmin țqeddimen mkul ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq, ma llan wid i ten-iḥesben d aklan-nsen. Ɣuṛ-sen zemren ad ssiwḍen ɣer lḥakem, ad ccetkin fell-asen ɣef tmanegt tameqqrant.
